author: Newt Gingrich
title: Newt Gingrich: Coronavirus spread because of Chinese government mismanagement, corruption and dishonesty
description: Watching the Chinese Communist dictatorship mismanage the initial coronavirus epidemic, cover it up and then lie about it has been infuriating. But it is also a good lesson in how dangerous and how profoundly dishonest the dictatorship is.
content:
